PrecisAmendment to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS SCHEDULE NO. 712 requiring the persons responsible for a drug to have the person's name and the address of the person's principal place of business in Canada appear on the inner and outer labels of the drug marketed in Canada, effective October 1, 1994.
